size.description_zh: 单元格大小，可选值为 large

icon.description: The icon name or image link on the left is equivalent to the [name attribute](https://vant-docs.netlify.app/#/en-US/icon#props) of the Icon component.
icon.description_zh: 左侧图标名称或图片链接，等同于 Icon 组件的 [name 属性](https://vant-docs.netlify.app/#/zh-CN/icon#props)

icon-prefix.description: Icon class name prefix, equivalent to the [class-prefix property](https://vant-docs.netlify.app/#/en-US/icon#props) of the Icon component
icon-prefix.description_zh: 图标类名前缀，等同于 Icon 组件的 [class-prefix 属性](https://vant-docs.netlify.app/#/zh-CN/icon#props)

tag.description: The HTML tag name corresponding to the root node
tag.description_zh: 根节点对应的 HTML 标签名

url.description: The link address that you will be directed to after clicking
url.description_zh: 点击后跳转的链接地址

to.description: Click to jump to the destination route object, which is equivalent to the [to property](https://router.vuejs.org/zh/api/interfaces/RouterLinkProps.html#Properties-to) of the Vue Router.
to.description_zh: 点击后跳转的目标路由对象，等同于 Vue Router 的 [to 属性](https://router.vuejs.org/zh/api/interfaces/RouterLinkProps.html#Properties-to)

border.description: Whether to display the inner border

replace.description: Whether to replace the current page history when redirecting
replace.description_zh: 是否在跳转时替换当前页面历史

clickable.description: Whether to turn on click feedback

is-link.description: Whether to show the right-hand arrow and turn on click feedback
is-link.description_zh: 是否展示右侧箭头并开启点击反馈

required.description: Whether or not to display a form required asterisk
required.description_zh: 是否显示表单必填星号

center.description: Whether to center the content vertically

arrow-direction.description_zh: 箭头方向，可选值为 `left` `up` down

title-style.description: Extra styling for the header on the left

title-class.description: Additional class names in the header on the left

value-class.description: The content on the right side has an additional class name

events.name: click
events.description: Triggered when a cell is clicked

slots.name: title
slots.description: Customize the title on the left

slots.name: value
slots.description: Customize the content on the right

slots.name: label
slots.description: Customize the description below the title
slots.description_zh: 自定义标题下方的描述信息

slots.name: icon
slots.description: Customize the icon on the left

slots.name: right-icon
slots.description: Customize the icon on the right

slots.name: extra

slots.description_zh: 自定义单元格最右侧的额外内容
